task.summary: Initial implementation of SocialGraph with added degree centrality tracking and supporting unit tests
Added automatic sorting by centrality and retrieval of X top nodes
Bug fix: prevent duplication of vertices in centrality index after increment and use descending order on index to get top number
Bug fix: need to work with List as return value of random vertices retrieval
Friends Paradox: get random friend of random node implementation
Initial implementation of Spread modeling algorithm - interface and SocialSpread abstract class
Initial implementation of AbsoluteSocialSpread - one node is required to start a spread. Each step all "friends" are "infected"
Additional test case to confirm correct step counting
Add SpreadRunner to control and run the experiments with sensors detecting spreads

Basic experiment with one sensor and one source of spread.
Random sensor, avg steps: 3.04 Centrality sensor, avg steps: 1.94 Friends sensor, avg steps: 2.85
Expose more controls over the experiment
